Uber has partnered with Travelstart to launch “UberESCAPE”, offering users the opportunity to purchase selected flights for R99 between 9-11 May 2018. “From today, riders need to log into the Uber app to purchase a one-way flight to cities such as Johannesburg, Cape Town, Durban, and Port Elizabeth,” said Uber. “Flights must be booked and paid for through the Travelstart website accessible on the Uber app.” Users will also receive R400 worth of Uber rides for each flight purchased. The steps to take advantage of the promotion are detailed below: